title: LiveEdutvICO
author: LiveEdutvICO
content: Education Ecosystem is offering an amazing $10,000 worth of $LEDU token  to its community users for the upcoming launch of its Native App. The bounty program is to be for a period of 3 weeks. Users are expected to complete all task. Data from the doc form will be taken every Friday of the week till expiration of the bounty.
